value: Breeds from the upper Argun River in Transbaikalia, northeastern Mon- golia and southern Manchuria, south to India, Ceylon, Burma, Siam, Indo- china and Hainan. On migration or in winter through the Malay Archi- pelago to Australia.

value: Indon, PNG, Sol, New Guinea, Bougainville, Buka, Misima, New Britain, New Guinea, New Hanover, New Ireland, Three Sisters
